posting_body: ['VIEW OUR WEBSITE:', '<URL>', 'Milehouse at Belleview Station, managed by Holland Residential', '6750 E Chenango Ave', 'Denver, CO 80237', 'show contact info', "MileHouse is the DTC's premier apartment community.", "You're just an elevator ride from retailers and the Belleview Light Rail Station.", '<URL>', 'This 657sf urban 1 bedroom is a perfect hybrid of a studio and a 1 bedroom.', 'Spacious walk in closet for all of you clothes or additional storage.', 'Corner style kitchen with ample counter top space for a leisurely cooking experience.', 'This apartment requires a $500 deposit.', 'Community Features', '* Professionally Managed', '* After-Hours Emergency Maintenance', '* Billiards', '* TV Lounge', '* Elevator', '* Controlled Access', '* Spa', '*', "Our prices can change daily, price listed is based on today's availability.", 'Call for details.', '* Fitness Studio', '* Hiking and Biking Trails', '* Short Term Lease Available', '* Dry Cleaning and Laundry Service', '* Make moving easy!', 'We give you access to the Updater service for free!', 'Complete your moving tasks with one simple tool!', '* Easy Freeway Access', '* Garage Parking', '* Minutes from Restaurants, Shopping, and Much More', '* Swimming Pool', '* Easy Access to Public Transportation', '* Covered Parking', '* Outdoor Grill Area', '* Controlled Access Parking', '* Community Kitchen', '* Extra Storage', '* Rooftop Terraces with Amazing Views', '* Short or Long Term Lease Available', '* Community Lounge', '* Smoke Free Community', '* Disability Access', '* Landscaped Courtyards', '* Roof Deck', '* Renters Insurance is Required', '* We are a social community!', 'Find our Yelp, Facebook or Twitter page online.', '* Non Smoking Community', '* Green Recycling Center', '* Liability Insurance is Required', '* WiFi Access', '* Package Acceptance', '* Sun Deck', '*', 'Special offers and pricing available to new leases only, not renewals, transfers or current residents', '[#9340916]']
